{"tid":383261,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[地盤撚]電燈定冷氣","createTime":"2017-09-01T10:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T12:06:03.000Z","uid":98473,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3cdd289030749db8a4b48991d4cbe90b6efdd876","tid":383261,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"自己撈左五年釘板<br />\n無錯係人工高 但真係好辛苦<br />\n而自己都己經三十二歲 唔想未來既日子都做釘板<br />\n唔係真係有錢冇命洗<br />\n想轉返啲比較小體力勞動<br />\n先唔理人工 大家覺得電燈定冷氣好撈<br />\n因為我唔想成世都做地盤 想未來做埋樓宇維修<br />\n你地認為邊行好d<br />\n而我暫時只對依兩行有興趣"},{"pid":"2322340a5ae913d8a99c24af8e34a8dce8d369be","tid":383261,"uid":41772,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"咁都要問人？ 想做咩就做咩"},{"pid":"e9ced25e65bf5bbd078bac49db383e1019196401","tid":383261,"uid":39853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"做冷氣可以食咖喱<br />\n申利：做冷氣"},{"pid":"2106fdea25e0b44eeddf52f053324121e84bc082","tid":383261,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都要問人？ 想做咩就做咩</blockquote><br />\n就係兩行都有興趣 但又唔知邊個前途好d<br />\n想聽下人意見姐"},{"pid":"341c69105687847921f9d7f59b1f64f01b40cc67","tid":383261,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做冷氣可以食咖喱<br />\n申利：做冷氣</blockquote><br />\n我都聽過 而冇老盤撈又可以跑街好似幾好<br />\n同埋冷氣需求好似大d<br />\n但冷氣佬風火水電都要識d 好雜"},{"pid":"e6c4aafd55dec2e0886609ac0d8628b1cffc8c03","tid":383261,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"defed29888390b82f256e7d9395ab30d184e8796","tid":383261,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電燈有毅力可以慢慢讀上去 讀到碩士都得   冷氣未聽過有冷氣學士  不過最後都係要讀番書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得好撚岩 冷氣連公會都好似電"},{"pid":"23e8387b87c4459a3ae209d08609db441f2f4013","tid":383261,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>電燈有毅力可以慢慢讀上去 讀到碩士都得   冷氣未聽過有冷氣學士  不過最後都係要讀番書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得好撚岩 冷氣連公會都好似冇</blockquote>"},{"pid":"850aa6f59dd758acd76f7629b3cfb6cbd22aacc0","tid":383261,"uid":39853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:22:13.000Z","msg":"做冷氣冇冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccffbef8da1d71b1cc33e4a0a6ae89d8e41fb53","tid":383261,"uid":123576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ed9c2eae6c856c8b36113ee5b6a8db59ba91882","tid":383261,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T18:34:18.000Z","msg":"電"},{"pid":"78518aedc4484f320b39ceb3489ebdb960b62383","tid":383261,"uid":117647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電燈有毅力可以慢慢讀上去 讀到碩士都得   冷氣未聽過有冷氣學士  不過最後都係要讀番書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得好撚岩 冷氣連公會都好似冇</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦 自己google下先啦"},{"pid":"d9769a1b2397d5812f8b27843871f7591a836bbb","tid":383261,"uid":29523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電燈有毅力可以慢慢讀上去 讀到碩士都得   冷氣未聽過有冷氣學士  不過最後都係要讀番書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得好撚岩 冷氣連公會都好似冇</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦 自己google下先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚柒蠢，冷氣佬無工會都講得出，咪撚點醒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9526f56609f1ea912e4bb3399c434573b803896","tid":383261,"uid":117647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"自己做下research先啦<br />\n香港邊度會有科叫電燈學士 冷氣學士啊<i